ed start\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"Broadbridge\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"the poster\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"a silhouette\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"Broadbridge\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Broadbridge denied she would ever do that, adding, \\\"She does not need me to do that.\\\")\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Broadbridge\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Broadbridge, Gunn's lawyers also forbade her from doing Raygun's infamouskangaroo dance, which Gunn apparently owns.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.7791218374023712, \"rank\": 0.28296785077555286, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.246819764023135e-26, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.7791218374023712, \"rank\": 0.28296785077555286, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Broadbridge\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That one did puzzle me,\\\" Broadbridge quipped.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That one\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"Broadbridge\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean, that's an Olympic leveldance.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic leveldance\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How would I possibly be able to do that without any formal break dancing training?\\\"\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any formal break dancing training\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, for her part,saidher lawyers stepped in out of concern the public would associate her with the musical.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.7791218374023712, \"rank\": 0.28296785077555286, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her part\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"saidher lawyers\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also cleared up some of the trademark issues, saying she owns the rights to her name and her \\\"famous kangaroo silhouette pose\\\" but denied any ownership of the kangaroo dance itself.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trademark issues\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the rights\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"famous kangaroo silhouette pose\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"any ownership\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the kangaroo dance\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She said the reason she trademarked the silhouette was \\\"because we were notified other parties applied to trademark my name and image for commercial purposes.\\